data.description: Price IMPROVED! Welcome to this updated and well cared for home in the heart of Nampa.  This warm and welcoming house has the desirable split bedroom floor plan with an upstairs bonus room.  The spacious and open floor plan with new flooring throughout has vaulted ceilings and is wonderful for entertaining.  Enjoy cooking in this fabulous kitchen with your gas range and new cabinets.  Large master bedroom boasts two closets and a soaking tub. Beautifully landscaped yard with cement curbing, storage shed and space for RV parking. Newer HVAC system and water softener. Don't miss out on this lovely, move-in ready home.
